data.name: Spicy Tomato and Avocado Toast
data.quickTastyDescription: A fresh and zesty twist on classic toast, topped with creamy avocado and spicy tomatoes for a delightful kick.
detailedCookingInstructions: Toast the slices of whole grain bread until golden brown.
While the bread is toasting, slice the cherry tomatoes in half and place them in a bowl.
Add olive oil, lemon juice, salt, black pepper, and red chili flakes to the tomatoes and mix well.
In a separate bowl, mash the ripe avocado with a fork, adding a pinch of salt and a dash of lemon juice to taste.
Spread the mashed avocado evenly on the toasted bread slices.
Top the avocado with the spicy tomato mixture, ensuring an even distribution.
Serve immediately and enjoy your zesty toast!
data.modifiersForBase: Topped with spicy tomatoes and creamy avocado
